reviewText: Wow!!! Awesome deal. Love it and so does the kid
Cant beat the price for 3 movies.

My son loves all 3 movies. My son is 4. We used to have all the movies but his father lost all of them:( So, Im sitting here on Amazon trying to re-buy all his favorites. This 3 movie disk is way worth it!
Great price for three movies! I bought these for my nephews and they were a hit!
Nothing to complain about.  Robots is the ish.  R.I.P. Robin Williams.
